<body>
<p>NOTE: At a minimum, supply the values indicated in <span class="required">red</span></p>
<p class="required">Choose a universe: vanilla, grid, standard or parallel
<input type="text" id="tuniverse" size=8 maxlength="8"></p>
<a href="/bin/view/Sandbox/FileGen#universes" class="twikiCurrentTopicLink twikiAnchorLink">Help me choose!</a>
<p id=enterURL>if you want to use one specific grid resource, enter the url here:
<input type="text" id="resURL" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p class="required">What's the name of your executable file? (include file extension) <input type="text" id="executable" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p>If you're going to pass any arguments to your executable, enter arguments:
<input type="text" id="arguments" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p class="required">Choose a name (and directory, if desired) for your logfile or logfiles:
<input type="text" id="logfile" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p class="required">Choose a name (and directory, if desired) for your output file or files:
<input type="text" id="outfile" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p class="required">Choose a name (and directory if desired) for your error file or error files:
<input type="text" id="errfile" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<a href="/bin/view/Sandbox/FileGen#how_to_separate_multiple_output" class="twikiCurrentTopicLink twikiAnchorLink">How do I separate multiple log, output and error files?</a>
<p>Specify any other input files, if applicable:
<input type="text" id="iptfiles" size=50 maxlength="50"></p>
<p>Specify any other output files, if applicable:
<input type="text" id="optfiles" size=50 maxlength="50">  </p>  
<a href="/bin/view/Sandbox/FileGen#when_to_specify_output_files" class="twikiCurrentTopicLink twikiAnchorLink">When do I need to use this?</a>
<p>Maximum anticipated memory usage (specify KB, MB, GB or TB):
<input type="text" id="maxmem" size=7 maxlength="7"></p>
<p>Maximum anticipated disk usage (specify KB, MB, GB or TB):
<input type="text" id="maxdisk" size=7 maxlength="7"></p>
<p>Number of CPUs you're requesting (only necessary for parallel jobs):
<input type="text" id="maxcpu" size=2 maxlength="2"></p>
<a href="/bin/view/Sandbox/FileGen#how_to_determine_resource_needs" class="twikiCurrentTopicLink twikiAnchorLink">how do I determine what I will need?</a>
<p>How many times would you like to run this job, if more than one?
<input type="text" id="runNum" size=5 maxlength="5"></p>
<button onclick="createSubFile()">Create this submit file</button>
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="After_clicking_the_button_the_su"></a> After clicking the button, the submit file appears below </span></h2>
<p id=subUniverse></p>
<p id=subResource></p>
<p id=subExecutable></p>
<p id=subArguments></p>
<p id=subLogs></p>
<p id=subOuts></p>
<p id=subErrs></p>
<p id=subIpts></p>
